{"tid":934041,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"（無圖） 頭先食牛雜粉， 串到個阿姐一棵都無","createTime":"2018-12-09T03:19:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-09T10:45:53.000Z","uid":34571,"like":79,"dislike":538,"uniUserReply":51,"replies":[{"pid":"1a16435cda10412614495e30f0b66abab74f1f85","tid":934041,"uid":34571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T03:19:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 大陸口音阿姐<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 廚房仔<br />\n<br />\n是咁的，咁我去到就叫咗碗牛雜粉， 食食下就聽到啲阿姐係度講野<br />\n<br />\n阿姐：微訊好用過whatsapp 好多， 睇野又詳細啲， 多啲野睇<br />\n<br />\n廚房仔：咩呀， whatsapp 好用啲喎<br />\n<br />\n阿姐： 我地中國人，係用微訊既， 唔用鬼佬野<br />\n<br />\n咁我時完就陰陰嘴笑， 繼續食野， 到我食完比錢果陣<br />\n<br />\n我： 我地正常人， 係用telegram 既！！信就信， 唔信就唔信， 咩叫微信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n阿姐： <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之後我頭也不回，就行咗出去， 佢連搏我既機會都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54e8ffdfa1dc6705d391bdebd77f7d3ea84f03c6","tid":934041,"uid":17496,"like":104,"dislike":1,"score":103,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T03:21:02.000Z","msg":"閱"},{"pid":"72da4384cb7441b7bff5467e36e4634d0494d1af","tid":93404